    <text id="F0009T">
        <front id="d2">
            <div1 type="summary" id="d3">
                <p>Potter writes to his wife of how much he loves her and longs to be reunited with
                    his family.</p>
            </div1>
        </front>

        <body id="d4">
            <div1 type="letter" id="d5">
                

                <opener>
                  
                    <salute>Dear Cynthia</salute>
                </opener>

                <p>I have <orig reg="tried">tired</orig> to give you as faithful a picture of how I
                    am getting along as possible as this. There is only one drawback &amp; that
                    is my wife is far away from me. I <orig reg="can't">cant</orig> enjoy the
                    pleasure of her company as I would wish <orig reg="to">too</orig> but I still
                    live on hope. In thought I am there all the time hearing your voice &amp;
                    enjoying your caress. It would be the sweetest enjoyment in the world for me to
                    be back at home with you now once more &amp; it is that hope that keeps me
                    from becoming downspirited. I will see my wife after a while, so I will wait on.
                    Hope on love &amp; a kind Creator will bless me in giving my loved ones to
                    me again. Join with me in prayer Cynthia to Him who rules all that He may permit
                    us to meet again that we may enjoy ourselves in love &amp; prepare ourselves
                    &amp; children for his kingdom in Heaven. Kiss all children <orig reg="for"
                        >fo</orig> your affectionate husband</p>

                <closer>
                    <salute>Kiss all the children for your affectionate husband</salute>
                    <signed>S. M. Potter</signed>
                    <seg type="postscript">Our paymaster has not come yet. Would you send me a few
                        postage stamps in your next</seg>
                </closer>
            </div1>
        </body>
    </text>
